The service, the knowledge, personal and individual care I received was unmatched. John helped me strategize and negotiate for a raise as my job and it worked!! Highly recommend using them. 10/10

originalText.text: If you’re considering working with Five Star Resume, my advice is to stop reading this review, and just do it. I had an absolutely amazing experience working with John at FSR! I was struggling to effectively tell my professional story through my resume, which is what led me to search for a resume writing service. I compared many different options on the market, and I believe that the value you get from FSR is INCREDIBLE. Their packages aren't based on a set number of phone calls or revisions – they are based on getting to a finished product that you’re thrilled with. As a result, you get so much deep, individualized attention – from an initial in-depth phone consultation, to multiple rounds of revisions, to one-off phone calls along the way to talk through the process. Working with John was amazing – his organization and communication is stellar, and he did a great job of guiding me while also being open to my thoughts and feedback. Within 2 weeks of our first call I had an updated resume that showcases my experience and accomplishments so much better, and within 3 months of that, I received an offer for a dream job. I’m so grateful to John and Five Star Resume, and would wholeheartedly recommend FSR to any job seeker!
